text: José Márquez may refer to: * José Ignacio de Márquez (1793–1880), Colombian statesman, lawyer, and professor * Jose Midas Marquez (born 1966), court administrator and the Supreme Court spokesperson of the Philippines * José Guadarrama Márquez ( 1978–2012), Mexican politician * José Jesús Márquez ( 1994–1998), Spanish taekwando fighter * Joseph Marquez (born 1991), professional Super Smash Bros. Melee player ==See also== * José Marques da Silva (1869–1947), Portuguese architect and educator * Josue Marquez (1946–2018), Puerto Rican boxer
